message: Added workspace context

Running command: set -e
WORKDIR="/workspace"
if [ ! -d "$WORKDIR" ]; then
  echo "Directory $WORKDIR not found" >&2
  exit 1
fi
REMOTE_BASE="http://the-agent-company.com:8092/remote.php/dav/files/theagentcompany/Documents"
USER="theagentcompany"
PASS="theagentcompany"
LOGFILE="/tmp/owncloud_upload.log"
: > "$LOGFILE"
# Ensure remote base exists
curl -u "$USER:$PASS" -X MKCOL "$REMOTE_BASE" -s -S >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1 || true
# Create directories
find "$WORKDIR" -type d -print0 | while IFS= read -r -d '' dir; do
  rel="${dir#$WORKDIR}"
  # remove leading slash
  rel="${rel#/}"
  if [ -z "$rel" ]; then
    remote_dir="$REMOTE_BASE"
  else
    # URL-encode the path
    enc=$(python3 - <<PY
import urllib.parse,sys
p=sys.argv[1]
print('/'.join(urllib.parse.quote(part) for part in p.split('/')))
PY
 "$rel")
    remote_dir="$REMOTE_BASE/$enc"
  fi
  echo "MKCOL $remote_dir" >> "$LOGFILE"
  curl -u "$USER:$PASS" -X MKCOL "$remote_dir" -s -S >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1 || true
done
# Upload files
find "$WORKDIR" -type f -print0 | while IFS= read -r -d '' file; do
  rel="${file#$WORKDIR/}"
  enc=$(python3 - <<PY
import urllib.parse,sys
p=sys.argv[1]
print('/'.join(urllib.parse.quote(part) for part in p.split('/')))
PY
 "$rel")
  remote_url="$REMOTE_BASE/$enc"
  echo "PUT $remote_url" >> "$LOGFILE"
  # Use curl to upload
  curl -u "$USER:$PASS" -T "$file" "$remote_url" -s -S >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1 || {
    echo "Failed to upload $file to $remote_url" >> "$LOGFILE"
  }
done
echo "Upload finished. Log at $LOGFILE"
ls -lh "$LOGFILE" || true
cat "$LOGFILE" | sed -n '1,200p'
